        </div>
        <section class="l-section l-section--solutions">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="l-row">
                    <div class="l-col-xs-12-of-12" data-aos="fade-up">
                        <div class="o-heading">
                            <span class="o-heading__subtitle">the solutions</span>
                            <h2 class="o-heading__title">What can we do to alleviate the effects of climate change?</h2>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="l-row">
                    <div class="l-col-xs-12-of-12 l-col-md-6-of-12 l-col-lg-4-of-12" data-aos="fade">
                        <div class="c-solution">
                            <span class="c-solution__icon icon-sun"></span>
                            <h3 class="c-solution__title">Adopt renewable energies</h3>
                            <p>Greenhouse gases, such as oil and gas, destroy our planet and make us sick.  As suggested by <a href="http://www.greenpeace.org/usa/">Greenpeace</a>, we must switch to cleaner, renewable sources of energy such as wind, solar, and geothermal.<sup><a href="#footer">[10]</a></sup></p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="l-col-xs-12-of-12 l-col-md-6-of-12 l-col-lg-4-of-12" data-aos="fade" data-aos-delay="300">
                        <div class="c-solution">
                            <span class="c-solution__icon icon-bus"></span>
                            <h3 class="c-solution__title">Utilize green transport</h3>
                            <p>Instead of riding in cars, <a href="http://www.greenpeace.org/usa/">Greenpeace</a> suggests that individuals walk, bike, carpool, use public transport, or purchase an electric vehicle.  Greenpeace asserts that electric vehicles are becoming more advanced and affordable.<sup><a href="#footer">[5]</a></sup></p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="l-col-xs-12-of-12 l-col-md-6-of-12 l-col-lg-4-of-12" data-aos="fade" data-aos-delay="450">
                        <div class="c-solution">
                            <span class="c-solution__icon icon-lightbulb"></span>
                            <h3 class="c-solution__title">Save energy</h3>
                            <p><a href="http://www.greenpeace.org/usa/">Greenpeace</a> believes that turning off unoccupied electronics and using energy efficient lighting can alleviate climate change.  Such energy efficient lighting includes LEDs, compact fluorescents, and halogen incandescents.<sup><a href="#footer">[5]</a></sup></p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="l-col-xs-12-of-12 l-col-md-6-of-12 l-col-lg-4-of-12" data-aos="fade" data-aos-delay="300">
                        <div class="c-solution">
                            <span class="c-solution__icon icon-recycle"></span>
                            <h3 class="c-solution__title">Recycle materials</h3>
                            <p>The <a href="https://www.epa.gov/">EPA</a> says there are many benefits to recycling such as reducing landfill waste, conserving natural resources, preventing the collection of new raw materials, and overall, conserving energy.<sup><a href="#footer">[4]</a></sup></p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="l-col-xs-12-of-12 l-col-md-6-of-12 l-col-lg-4-of-12" data-aos="fade" data-aos-delay="450">
                        <div class="c-solution">
                            <span class="c-solution__icon icon-droplet"></span>
                            <h3 class="c-solution__title">Conserve water</h3>
                            <p>Conserving water saves energy, which in turn reduces the abundance of greenhouse gases in the atmosphere.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="l-col-xs-12-of-12 l-col-md-6-of-12 l-col-lg-4-of-12" data-aos="fade" data-aos-delay="600">
                        <div class="c-solution">
                            <span class="c-solution__icon icon-person"></span>
                            <h3 class="c-solution__title">Volunteer and donate</h3>
                            <p>There are many nonprofits that contribute to beach and waterway clean ups.  You can also donate to nonprofits such as the <a href="https://www.nrdc.org/">NRDC</a>.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
