                        <h2 class="l-section__title">We can help our planet</h2>
                        <p>Based on the evidence provided above, it is clear that we are the problem; however, we can also be the solution.  Simply by doing a few of the things listed above, such as recycling and riding your bike, you can help make the world a cleaner place—the planet will love you for it!</p>
